    <section>
        <h2>Signs Your Property Needs Urgent Waterproofing</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Efflorescence:</strong> White, salty powder deposits on walls.</li>
                <li><strong>Capillary Rise:</strong> Damp patches climbing up from the floor.</li>
                <li><strong>Musty Odors:</strong> Hidden mold growth behind storage or panels.</li>
                <li><strong>Wall Blistering:</strong> Paint peeling or bubbling due to trapped moisture.</li>
            </ul>
